GraphMSPOption, TriMSPOption
public abstract class MSPOption
extends javax.swing.JToolBar

This Panel is shown on the right border if on the main frame some solutions or kernel elements are displayed. It provides some buttons for further analysis of the kernel or solution elements. It is possible to add some, to show all kernel elements and to check whether the chosen elements are linear independent. The subclasses can add further methods.

Author:
Irene Thesing
